<note n="0116008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116008">優陀耶＝憂陀耶【宮】</note>
<note n="0116009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116009">殼＝<g ref="#CB00592">㲉</g>【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0116010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116010">如＝故【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0116011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116011">和尚＝和上【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
