<note n="0117001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117001">施＝捨【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0117002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117002">以何＝何以【明】</note>
<note n="0117003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117003">唯＝惟【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0117004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117004">誦＝頌【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0117005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117005">（即）＋自憶念【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0117006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117006">喜＝善【三】</note>
<note n="0118001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118001">二＝一【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0118002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118002">馬＋（力）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0118003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118003">牛＋（力）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0118004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118004">此＝比【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0118005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118005">角＝捔【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0118006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118006">硬＝鞕【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0118007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118007"><g ref="#CB00687">𦼮</g>＝幹【三】，擀【宮】</note>
<note n="0118008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118008">（身）＋力【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0119001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119001">婆＝娑【宮】</note>
<note n="0119002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119002">延＝旬【明】＊</note>
<note n="0119003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119003">各＋（自）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0119004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119004">益＝蓋【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0119005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119005">言＝曰【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0120001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0120001">瑣＝鎖【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0120002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0120002">一＝二【宋】</note>
<note n="0120003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0120003">俱＋（者）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0120004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0120004">卷第二十二終【三】【宮】</note>
