<note n="0120007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0120007">宿命智＝力如宿【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0121001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121001">辦＝辯【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0121002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121002">爾＝念【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0121003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121003">此＝生【三】【宮】</note>
